{"tid":2008214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商家幾時反抗，去便利店買野比錢都話犯限聚令，咁仲有人出街鳩嗚?","createTime":"2020-05-09T01:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T01:13:43.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c598f4bb9059113d30952a67f459784a6d7113f1","tid":2008214,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:13:43.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n8 hrs &middot; <br />\n李小姐與伍先生兩人在通菜街一間便利店購物後，排隊第一名準備付款。防暴警突然出現，命令店內所有顧客到外邊截查，並一律票控違反限聚令。收到告票的李小姐自問沒有違反法律，打算向區議員求助，拒絕票控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3063143490437917/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3063143490437917%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=5197ace5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3063143490437917/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/97129892_3063143450437921_3177386083679731712_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=iKg3-aIa8mcAX_jwszL&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=a10412751e78fe93d5617bc3429f05f7&amp;oe=5EDAADDF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F97129892_3063143450437921_3177386083679731712_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DiKg3-aIa8mcAX_jwszL%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Da10412751e78fe93d5617bc3429f05f7%26oe%3D5EDAADDF&h=e7019114&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}